\pard\f0\fs28 Umbel of 4-9 flowers; spathe 2-valved. Flowers greenish-white, erect, stellate. Hypanthial tube and corona absent. Filaments as long as anthers or somewhat shorter. Capsule depressed-globose; perianth dry; seeds few.
